{"tid":776244,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人為咗追求心上人而做啲自己從來唔會做嘅嘢？","createTime":"2018-08-12T00:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T05:25:12.000Z","uid":143093,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8a2dd7ab5301d864e2918570cdfd2fea01abe3","tid":776244,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n我係個極怕熱同極大汗又唔鍾意出街嘅人，宜家咁嘅天氣我平時絕對唔會出，但為咗想見到佢兩眼就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n激嬲咗佢，我心掛掛咗幾日，我究竟走去買嘢送比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我平時連禮物都極少送嘅人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時唔會突登去主動撩人講嘢，為咗佢就日日搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咁多佢都係唔get<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知係咪扮啦 我放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b721d2e43a1afa5f2f60f28fbc000047e7b327b","tid":776244,"uid":197135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"你做啲好平常炸喎對平常人嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都試過你第二同第三個例子 對初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0982922ec5c0742fa1fa521ed02a970c9c1fe4","tid":776244,"uid":103777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"咁卑躬屈膝已經輸左"},{"pid":"3c48456c5c91b812b936c9d812b55a6ea831f520","tid":776244,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b721d2e43a1afa5f2f60f28fbc000047e7b327b","tid":776244,"uid":197135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"你做啲好平常炸喎對平常人嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都試過你第二同第三個例子 對初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:48:35.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣<br />\n我唔會照顧人<br />\n但心上人飲醉酒，我衝咗去佢屋企照顧咗佢成晚無瞓過覺，用手接佢嘅嘔吐物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159ce966a3c0cc916a5e422582d81bd00cb224f6","tid":776244,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b721d2e43a1afa5f2f60f28fbc000047e7b327b","tid":776244,"uid":197135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"你做啲好平常炸喎對平常人嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都試過你第二同第三個例子 對初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"同上面個幾點我係同佢識咗無幾耐就咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬平時嘅我邊會對啲啱啱識嘅人咁做"},{"pid":"d48f735ddc44f5b67084e9dd4c6886f0a6167c39","tid":776244,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"人地唔係get唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08382b3491cb7d6d1b7fcbf99a459f155c3257ad","tid":776244,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:27:37.000Z","msg":"放囉<br />\n冇人會在意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa731c520a2c6c4c5e979fd28842c47a4ae08c6","tid":776244,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<br />\n傾電話<br />\n出街<br />\n食飯<br />\n睇戲<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味我完全無朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}